{"title": "梦的解析", "index": 1, "content": [{"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_9363b74291.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "图书在版编目（CIP）数据"}, {"type": "text", "value": "梦的解析/（奥）弗洛伊德著；殷世钞译．--南昌：江西人民出版社，2014.7"}, {"type": "text", "value": "ISBN 978-7-210-06490-9"}, {"type": "text", "value": "Ⅰ．①梦…　Ⅱ．①弗…　②殷…　Ⅲ．①梦－精神分析　Ⅳ．①B845.1"}, {"type": "text", "value": "中国版本图书馆CIP数据核字（2014）第129817号"}, {"type": "text", "value": "梦的解析"}, {"type": "text", "value": "（奥）西格蒙德·弗洛伊德　著　殷世钞　译"}, {"type": "text", "value": "江西人民出版社出版发行"}, {"type": "text", "value": "地址：江西省南昌市三经路47号附1号（邮编：330006）"}, {"type": "text", "value": "编辑部电话：0791-86898980"}, {"type": "text", "value": "发行部电话：0791-86898801"}, {"type": "text", "value": "网址：www.jxpph.com"}, {"type": "text", "value": "E-mail：jxpph@tom.com　web@jxpph.com"}, {"type": "text", "value": "2014年8月第1版　2014年8月第1次印刷"}, {"type": "text", "value": "开本：710毫米×1000毫米　1/16"}, {"type": "text", "value": "印张：23　插页：8"}, {"type": "text", "value": "字数：440千字"}, {"type": "text", "value": "ISBN 978-7-210-06490-9"}, {"type": "text", "value": "赣版权登字—01—2014—249"}, {"type": "text", "value": "版权所有　侵权必究"}, {"type": "text", "value": "定价：39.80元"}, {"type": "text", "value": "承印厂：香河县宏润印刷有限公司"}, {"type": "text", "value": "目录"}, {"type": "text", "value": "前言"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第一章　关于梦的问题的科学文献"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第一节　梦与清醒状态的关系"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第二节　梦的材料：梦中的记忆"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第三节　梦的刺激和来源"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第四节　为什么人醒来后就忘记做了什么梦"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第五节　梦的心理特征"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第六节　梦中的道德感"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第七节　关于梦的理论和功能"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第八节　梦与精神疾病的关系"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第二章　梦的解析方法：对一个梦例的分析"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第三章　梦是欲望的满足"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第四章　梦的伪装"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第五章　梦的材料和来源"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第一节　梦中最近的和无关紧要的材料"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第二节　梦的来源：童年经历"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第三节　梦的躯体刺激来源"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第四节　典型梦"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第六章　梦的运作"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第一节　压缩工作"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第二节　移置工作"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第三节　梦的表现手段"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第四节　关于表现力的考虑"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第五节　梦的象征"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第六节　一些梦例：梦中的计算和讲话"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第七节　荒谬的梦：梦中的理智活动"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第八节　梦中的感情"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第九节　梦的再加工"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第七章　关于做梦过程的心理学理论"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第一节　梦的遗忘"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第二节　回归作用"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第三节　关于“欲望的满足”"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第四节　被梦唤醒——梦的功能——焦虑梦"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第五节　原初过程和续发过程：压抑"}, {"type": "text", "value": "第六节　潜意识和意识：现实"}, {"type": "text", "value": "返回总目录"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_3cb66149c1.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "弗洛伊德"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_f0cece069d.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1878年，弗洛伊德一家。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_1226a9fd1f.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "8岁的弗洛伊德与父亲在一起"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_25e4f8f077.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1884年，弗洛伊德跟未婚妻玛莎在一起。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_1d8527e2c3.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1905年，弗洛伊德与母亲和妻子在一起。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_26d3c45e88.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "25岁的弗洛伊德"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_3cea192cca.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1907年，弗洛伊德与荣格带着双方家人出去玩。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_c5b1ebf309.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1916年，弗洛伊德跟两个儿子马丁和恩斯特在一起。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_6e972c898a.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1920年，弗洛伊德与女儿安娜·弗洛伊德。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_5eefeed05b.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1926年，弗洛伊德跟母亲在维也纳。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_9c3224ab3e.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1928年，弗洛伊德与女儿安娜·弗洛伊德。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_f1d44e1495.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1938年，弗洛伊德伦敦之行。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_e92d262bcd.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1939年，弗洛伊德晚年照。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_d5141afdd3.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "尽管弗洛伊德是一位和平主义者，但他对于步枪和其他武器有着由衷的喜爱，从图中荣格勉为其难的表情看出，在这场狩猎的游戏中，他被捉了。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_c8766eea50.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1906年，弗洛伊德在荣格苏黎世的家中为荣格庆生。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_1387cec836.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1907年，弗洛伊德和荣格与友人在一起放松休憩。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_a136fd22f7.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1908年，弗洛伊德与荣格访问期间，在一家美国台球厅打台球。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_3ea100c3f3.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1909年，弗洛伊德和荣格在杜塞尔多夫附近的莱茵河岸捕捉比目鱼。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_af0581ede9.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1912年，弗洛伊德和荣格在一次糟糕的北极探险途中合照。"}, {"type": "image", "src": "/api/books/4fc33e4af5fb/image/4fc33e4af5fb_2ae11caeb6.webp", "alt": ""}, {"type": "text", "value": "1922年，弗洛伊德与其他精神分析学家。"}]}